                        span.packages-card__title Therapy Dog
                        span.packages-card__text Service dogs help with performing a function for a person that is limited by a disability.
                .packages-wrap
                    .packages-card
                        span.packages-card__text-title Partial List of Disabilities Covered
                    .packages-card
                        span.packages-card__text Mobility issues, visual impairment (blindness), hearing impairment (deafness), seizures, diabetes, PTSD, autism, epilepsy, multiple sclerosis (MS), and other physical/mental disabilities
                    .packages-card
