                        img(src="/assets/images/index/packages-no.svg")
                        a.packages-card__button(href="#") Get Started

    .certificate-wrapper
        .container
            .certificate-wrap
                .certificate-header
                    .certificate-header-text
                        span.certificate-header-text__title Real Identification Card and Certificate
                        span.certificate-header-text__description The Animal Identification Number is the equivalent of a social security number or vehicle identification number for animals.
                        a.first-screen__button(href="#") Register Now
                    span.certificate-img Certificate
                .certificate-items
                    .certificate-item
                        img(src="/assets/images/index/certificate1.svg")
                        span.certificate-item__title Identification Card
                        span.certificate-item__text Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry
                    .certificate-item
                        img(src="/assets/images/index/certificate2.svg")
                        span.certificate-item__title Registration Certificate
                        span.certificate-item__text Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry
                    .certificate-item
                        img(src="/assets/images/index/certificate3.svg")
                        span.certificate-item__title 24/7 Online Verification
                        span.certificate-item__text Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry
    .container
        .laws
            span.laws__title Understand the Laws
            span.laws__description It’s important to understand all laws and state regulation in regards to Service and Emotional Support animals. Know your rights!
            .laws-items
                .laws-item
                    .laws-item-header
                        img(src="/assets/images/index/laws1.svg")
                        span.laws-item-header__title Service Animal
                    span.laws-otem__text Under the ADA, State and local governments, businesses, and nonprofit organizations that serve the public generally must allow service animals to accompany people with disabilities in all areas of the facility where the public is allowed to go.
                .laws-item
                    .laws-item-header
                        img(src="/assets/images/index/laws2.svg")
                        span.laws-item-header__title ESA
                    span.laws-otem__text Under the FHA, a disability is defined as a physical or mental impairment which significantly limits a person’s major life activities. Even if a lease says "no pets" or restricts pets, landlords are required to make what is called a “reasonable accommodation” to allow pets who serve as assistance animals, which includes animals who provide emotional support.
    .choose-wrapper
        .container
            .choose-wrap
                span.choose__title.laws__title Why Choose Us?
                span.choose__description.laws__description By using Federal Dog Registry you can be confident that you can bring your animal with you anywhere you go.
                .choose-item
                    img(src="/assets/images/index/choose1.svg")
                    .choose-item-wrap
                        .choose-item-card.active
                            span.choose-item__title.js-choose Instant Registration
                            span.choose-item__text Service dogs help with performing a function for a person that is limited by a disability.
                        .choose-item-card
                            span.choose-item__title.js-choose Licensed Therapists in all 50 States
                            span.choose-item__text Service dogs help with performing a function for a person that is limited by a disability.
                        .choose-item-card
                            span.choose-item__title.js-choose 24/7 Online Registration Verification
                            span.choose-item__text Service dogs help with performing a function for a person that is limited by a disability.
                        .choose-item-card
                            span.choose-item__title.js-choose Valid in all 50 US States
                            span.choose-item__text Service dogs help with performing a function for a person that is limited by a disability.
    .flying-wrapper
        .container
            .flying-wrap
                .flying-text
                    span.flying-text__title.laws__title Flying with a Dog
                    span.flying-text__description.laws__description Travel with your animal by your side with no extra fees or restrictions. To learn more about specific airline requirements click the button down below.
                    a.first-screen__button(href="#") Learn More
                .flying-cards
                    img(src="/assets/images/index/flying1.svg").flyig-cards__img
                    img(src="/assets/images/index/flying2.svg").flyig-cards__img
                    img(src="/assets/images/index/flying3.svg").flyig-cards__img
                    img(src="/assets/images/index/flying4.svg").flyig-cards__img
    .container
        .title-wrapper
            span.title__title.laws__title Title
            .title-wrap
                .title-items
                    .title-item
                        .title-item__number 9.000+
